import React from 'react'
import { BrowserRouter as Router,  Route, Link } from "react-router-dom";
import { Navbar, Nav,Button, } from 'react-bootstrap'
import anasayfa from '../pages/anasayfa'
import hakkimizda from '../pages/hakkimizda'
import iletisim from '../pages/iletisim'


export default function header() {
    return (
        <>
                <Router>

                <Navbar bg="light" expand="lg">
                <Navbar.Brand href="#home">React-Bootstrap</Navbar.Brand>
                <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
                <Navbar.Collapse id="basic-navbar-nav">
                    <Nav className="mr-auto">
                    <Nav.Link href="#home">Home</Nav.Link>
                    <Nav.Link href="#link">Link</Nav.Link>
                    </Nav>
                    <Form inline>
                    <FormControl type="text" placeholder="Search" className="mr-sm-2" />
                    <Button variant="outline-success">Search</Button>
                    </Form>
                </Navbar.Collapse>
                </Navbar>


        <Container>
            <ButtonToolbar>
                <Button><Link to="/">Anasayfa</Link></Button> 
                <Button><Link to="/hakkimizda">Blog</Link></Button>
                <Button><Link to="/iletisim">Hakkımızda</Link></Button>
            </ButtonToolbar>
            <ButtonToolbar>
            <Button><Link to="/login">Giriş Yap</Link></Button>
            </ButtonToolbar>
        </Container>


   
         <main >
           <Route path="/anasayfa" component={anasayfa} />
           <Route path="/hakkimizda" component={hakkimizda} />
           <Route path="/iletisim" component={iletisim} />
        </main>

    </Router>
        </>
    )
}
